The paper deals with privacy risks posed by third-party apps on cloud platforms, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also analyzes user behavior and perception of privacy, which could fall under the categories of cyberpsychology (cs.CY) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also involves data analysis and insights, which could fall under the categories of information retrieval (cs.IR) and databases (cs.DB).
